<li>Dourish, P. 2006. Implications for design. In Proceedings of the SIGCHI Conference on Human Factors in Computing Systems. CHI '06, ACM, 541-550. DOI=<a href="http://doi.acm.org/10.1145/1124772.1124855"  target="_blank">http://doi.acm.org/10.1145/1124772.1124855</a></li>
